Class TLAssignment

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TLDeclaration

    public class TLAssignment
extends TLExpression
    TLElement that represents an assignment instruction. It's characterized by a variable (as TLVariable) and the value of the assignment (as TLExpression).
